<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263390>
    dc:description "PLATE 89. Fenimorea nivalis, new species. Figs. 1 – 3: holotype, off Cabo Frio, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil (MZSP 122067). Fig. 1: ventral, lateral & dorsal views; Fig. 2: enlarged view of protoconch (not to scale); Fig. 3: apical view, V = varix, L = edge of outer lip. Figs. 4 – 5, paratypes. Fig. 4: off Rio Grande do Norte, Brazil (UF 470315); Figs. 5 – 10: off Cabo Frio, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. Figs. 5 – 6: BMSM 14991; Figs. 7 – 10: ANSP 464963." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263390/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

